Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.78,0:00:11.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play this flute.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.82,0:00:15.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot bring such suffering\nto Maria.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.12,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yaku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.22,0:00:21.09,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We will have to rely on your\nsense of smell.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.19,0:00:23.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Shikima guards haven't\nreturned from their search...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.00,0:00:26.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and we still can't find\NMiko and Nin-Nin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.70,0:00:27.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.53,0:00:31.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to wait for\nthe full moon.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.38,0:02:18.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! See?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.21,0:02:21.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.82,0:02:26.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They smell alike.\NGood job!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.39,0:02:30.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was tough digging up this\ncherished collection.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ranjatai, the most famous\nsince the Muromachi Era.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.99,0:02:38.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ranjatai? What's that?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.63,0:02:40.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this incense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.43,0:02:44.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Buddhist temples kept\nits name a secret.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.87,0:02:49.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Ranjatai was a secret\npossession of Todai Temple.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.11,0:02:53.54,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was so treasured\nit never left temple.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A treasured incense?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No peeking!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.36,0:03:07.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look the other way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.53,0:03:09.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted a little whiff.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.59,0:03:13.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe the old\nlady actually had this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.80,0:03:16.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been passed\ndown from the Tensho era.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.54,0:03:22.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Recognizing it for the power\nthat it had...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.27,0:03:25.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...it's said that it was taken by\nthe Ashikaga Shogun...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.04,0:03:28.74,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and Nobunaga.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.28,0:03:34.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.35,0:03:35.32,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.42,0:03:38.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's another fragrance,\nbesides the incense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.26,0:03:40.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's making me crazy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.66,0:03:42.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:51.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This amorous fragrance must\nbe caused by the incense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't watch, Nin-Nin!\NI'm so embarrassed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.98,0:04:04.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do something!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do something?!\NWhat could I do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.39,0:04:12.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming! I'm coming!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another victim.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.84,0:04:25.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yaku.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.31,0:05:04.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime. My Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.34,0:05:06.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come back.\NCome back to me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.45,0:05:15.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime. Is it you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.78,0:05:45.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. This time\nyou won't get away!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.45,0:06:24.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Such weaklings. Is that the\nbest the Shikima can do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.06,0:06:36.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.97,0:06:39.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.50,0:06:44.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That flute can no longer\nharm us.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.88,0:06:48.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro now understands\nthat I didn't betray him.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.49,0:06:57.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.56,0:07:00.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki! Here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.26,0:07:06.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move! You're dealing\nwith the best of the Shikima!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.44,0:07:17.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think this is\njust a regular blow dart?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.69,0:07:31.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hesitate?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.56,0:07:34.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hesitate to use\nthe poison dart?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.34,0:07:52.37,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because deep in your heart\nyou want me to violate you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.31,0:07:54.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not true!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.69,0:08:04.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I should give you\nwhat you want.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.79,0:08:13.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The best of the Shikima\nis no match for me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.25,0:08:39.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Women are so wretched.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.79,0:08:44.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kill me instead of making me\nsuccumb to this perversion!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.86,0:08:50.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try. Let me give you\nwhat you really desire.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.44,0:09:01.64,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What such amorous\nconvulsions?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.91,0:09:32.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.94,0:09:35.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Warring States period!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.72,0:09:49.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddamn Danjo.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Danjo?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer needed.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.13,0:09:58.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bring your\nhead to the Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.57,0:10:02.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...and show them that I have\navenged your betrayal.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.35,0:10:12.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Spider Kettle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.39,0:10:18.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro, I took Shanahime\nfor my own.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.59,0:10:22.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will lay your place, with the\nbeauty of the 3,000 realms.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And I will take command\nof the Shikima realm!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Kyoshiro's alive,\NI can change the future!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.53,0:10:59.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa's possession will\nend if I save Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.36,0:11:01.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive Shanahime\nfor doing this to him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't forgive her.\NIt's all her fault!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro and Hidemasa\nwouldn't have been cursed...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.01,0:11:45.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...if it hadn't been for her.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fuck!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.62,0:11:58.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You fucking bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.49,0:12:00.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my member!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.60,0:12:10.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.57,0:12:14.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.27,0:12:17.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch, Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.94,0:12:22.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you swallow\nmy member!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.32,0:12:26.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to die\nso easily!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:31.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am a Shikima\nof great powers.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.52,0:12:36.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going to die.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With my blood...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.66,0:12:44.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...these will be cursed\nwith my hatred.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.77,0:12:49.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as this flute exists,\nas long as this kettle exists...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my hatred will\nremain forever.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.81,0:12:55.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gamara's to blame!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one that caused\nthis madness!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.13,0:13:18.57,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put an end to this evil,\nhere and now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The male flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.81,0:13:29.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The female flute!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.75,0:13:37.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.02,0:13:39.35,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.46,0:13:41.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where were you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.69,0:13:46.15,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I went back 400 years,\nto the Karimara fortress.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.77,0:13:48.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.80,0:13:51.63,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, and I was able to\nfind out the truth.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.74,0:13:53.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My father was wrong.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.97,0:13:58.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Chidori urn was\ngroaning and moaning away.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.04,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't leave it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.15,0:14:04.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was called back by the male\nand female flutes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just heard them too!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.08,0:14:08.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.35,0:14:09.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.35,0:14:11.84,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Fubuki and Yaku\nare okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.06,0:14:14.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko! Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.80,0:14:22.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yaku! Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.68,0:14:41.55,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,-Yaku!\N-Have they been killed?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.29,0:14:47.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin. You get Yaku!\NI'll get Fubuki!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.03,0:14:56.69,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake Fubuki up with that\nmedicine! I'll get Yaku!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.80,0:14:57.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.84,0:15:04.77,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.15,0:15:09.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness you're both\nall right!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.82,0:15:15.72,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You tricked us! You two\nwere just playing dead!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I failed! I can't face\nyou, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.76,0:15:22.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The female flute has been\ntaken!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.76,0:15:24.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the female and male flute\njust now...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.10,0:15:27.19,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've gone after the King!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.33,0:15:29.86,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just stand around!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The flutes again!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.94,0:15:37.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father! Mother!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.21,0:15:38.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did they do this?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.44,0:15:43.71,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They'll destroy the Shikima\nwith power of the flutes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.53,0:15:59.22,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Anti-Shikima are\nattacking!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.43,0:16:02.06,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Save the King and Maria!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.78,0:16:15.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, forgive me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.28,0:16:18.44,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot stop this curse\nof the Anti-Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.58,0:16:21.31,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.00,0:16:42.20,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,King! I resent\nwhat you've done to us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.31,0:16:45.47,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You drove apart our love\nwith your evil plot!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.58,0:16:46.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We won't forgive you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.08,0:16:49.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You deserve to be punished!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.71,0:16:51.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.05,0:16:56.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be punished by you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.45,0:16:59.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You have no shame!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.19,0:17:04.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shall suffer the wrath\nof our hatred.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.00,0:17:07.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've both fallen under the\ncurse of the Anti-Shikima.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.77,0:17:12.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't kill your mother,\nwho was my own sister!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.04,0:17:13.93,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.04,0:17:16.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro, don't be fooled\nby him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.07,0:17:20.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! You're under\nby the curse of the Kettle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.21,0:17:23.61,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to die!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.75,0:17:30.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to hurt\nsomeone, hurt me, not Maria.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.99,0:17:31.92,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darling!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.09,0:17:37.58,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How sweet. Showing off your\nlove while denying ours.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.23,0:17:41.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You can't kill me\nwith those flutes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Since your deaths, I became\NKing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.77,0:17:48.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As the Shikima King I can\nlive for 1 ,000 years.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.04,0:17:50.23,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then take the curse of\nthis flute for all of eternity.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.39,0:18:05.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to interfere?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.32,0:18:06.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.96,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I want\nto see your love realized.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.86,0:18:11.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.20,0:18:16.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the Shikima you\nshould bear a grudge against.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.53,0:18:21.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's a curse on the\NSpider Kettle and the flutes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're trying to trick us!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.74,0:18:28.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You two have returned to\nfulfill your love.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.75,0:18:31.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be tragic not to.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.69,0:18:40.49,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That fragrance.\NWhat is that incense?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.66,0:18:42.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.39,0:18:44.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That incense.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.06,0:18:47.79,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to Shanahime, who\nhas caused me such suffering.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.80,0:18:51.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.57,0:18:54.26,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the real Shanahime?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.37,0:18:57.70,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't bring\NHidemasa back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.81,0:19:01.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime! You're the real\none, aren't you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.58,0:19:05.98,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,-Miko!\N-Look out!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.49,0:19:19.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fubuki! Yaku!\NDon't hurt him!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.43,0:19:20.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the real one?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.63,0:19:25.66,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You wretch! Are you trying\nto steal my Kyoshiro?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.17,0:19:30.16,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just want to bring\NHidemasa back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.17,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.18,0:19:37.27,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.38,0:19:42.01,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot fulfill our purpose\nuntil the Shikima is ruined.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.95,0:19:46.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The truth! I want the truth!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.09,0:19:50.82,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The spell has clouded your\nmind! Listen to your heart!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.93,0:19:53.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you were the\NAnti-Shikima...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.13,0:19:55.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...Father, I mean the King...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...would use his power\nand destroy you both.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.03,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.14,0:20:01.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nonsense!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.61,0:20:03.13,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The reason he doesn't...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.24,0:20:06.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is that his sister is your\NMother, Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.61,0:20:11.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He is being merciful\nto you and your bride.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.62,0:20:12.51,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.62,0:20:14.85,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If he destroyed you,\nyou'd only come back.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.95,0:20:16.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But my Father...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.22,0:20:21.28,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...he didn't want to make you\nsuffer like that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.39,0:20:22.05,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.86,0:20:25.59,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your resentment\nonto me.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:28.89,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You will be gone, and I will\nforever bear your grievances.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.60,0:20:31.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.27,0:20:40.24,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye, my Hidemasa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.25,0:20:45.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're that woman!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.44,0:21:16.50,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget this hatred!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.61,0:21:18.95,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will not die now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.03,0:21:33.29,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.40,0:21:34.56,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.10,0:21:36.46,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.13,0:21:39.40,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.14,0:21:43.83,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko. Put the female and\nmale flutes inside it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.94,0:21:48.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only you understand them,\nand can break the curse.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.75,0:21:54.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.77,0:22:44.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've found our way.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.20,0:22:45.60,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.41,0:22:49.43,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.54,0:22:53.07,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At last, our love\ncan be fulfilled.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.68,0:22:57.41,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro, I'm so happy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.51,0:22:58.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shanahime.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.00,0:23:17.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoshiro, come to me!\NCome to me!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.04,0:23:55.94,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.74,0:24:00.90,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Miko.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.91,0:24:02.81,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your Majesty.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.91,0:24:05.68,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What will happen\nto Hidemasa?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.42,0:24:10.11,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Anti-Shikima curse is\nbroken, so he should be fine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.09,0:24:12.45,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.13,0:24:16.99,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.13,0:24:19.39,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:21.36,0:24:23.76,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Got to watch her. Nin-Nin!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.81,0:24:31.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:34.41,0:24:38.25,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how Miko's first\nlove will work out?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:38.35,0:24:42.34,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My hands are tied, even\nthough I'm the Shikima King.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:59.70,0:25:02.00,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A little sweet, don't you\nthink?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:03.44,0:25:06.53,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, as long as Hidemasa\nlikes them!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.88,0:25:16.18,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure was nice of Miko\nto invite me over.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.25,0:25:20.38,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're celebrating your\nrecovery! We were worried.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:20.49,0:25:25.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny though, I can't\nremember a thing.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.46,0:25:29.42,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All kinds of things happened\nto you. I'm glad you're okay.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.37,0:25:38.10,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurray for Miko's first love.\NBut I do envy the guy.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.71,0:25:39.80,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:39.91,0:25:42.14,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't forgotten our date,\nhave you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.81,0:25:46.78,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. I did forget.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:46.88,0:25:47.91,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So what's new.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.69,0:25:50.88,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You were supposed to meet\nmy Father!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.29,0:26:00.02,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was invited out by a cute\nfriend of mine.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.66,0:26:02.36,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So she's more important?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:02.47,0:26:04.73,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.Just a second.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:04.83,0:26:06.30,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-Nin?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:08.74,0:26:12.33,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's Miko going to do\nwhen she hears about this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:12.44,0:26:13.97,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell her!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:18.25,0:26:19.65,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hidemasa!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:20.88,0:26:23.48,Style1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see him!
